flowchart TD
    Dev([Developer pushes commit]) --> Hook{Pre-commit hook passes?}
    Hook -->|no| Reject[/Reject push locally/]
    Hook -->|yes| PR[Open pull request]
    PR --> CI{CI pipeline green?}
    CI -->|lint fails| Lint[Report lint errors]
    CI -->|tests fail| Tests[Report failing tests]
    Lint -.-> PR
    Tests -.-> PR
    CI -->|all checks pass| Review{Two approvals?}
    Review -->|changes requested| PR
    Review -->|approved| Merge[[Squash and merge to main]]
    Merge --> Build[Build release artifact]
    Build --> Store[(Artifact registry)]
    Store --> Stage[Deploy to staging]
    Stage --> Smoke{Smoke tests pass?}
    Smoke -->|no| Rollback[Roll back staging]
    Rollback -.-> Store
    Smoke -->|yes| Canary[Canary rollout 5 percent]
    Canary --> Metrics{Error rate under threshold?}
    Metrics -->|regression detected| Halt[Halt and page on-call]
    Halt -.->|incident opened| Rollback
    Metrics -->|healthy| Full[Promote to full production]
    Full --> Notify[Notify release channel]
    Notify --> Done((Release complete))
    Halt -->|postmortem| Retro[/Schedule retrospective/]
